    title Bookflix - Read Book, Magazine Online, Rate Book, Magazine Online

  body

    header.showcase
      .showcase-top
        img(src='/uploads/logo/logoUpdate.png', alt='Bookflix')
        a.btn.btn-rounded(href='#') Sign in
      .showcase-content
        h1 Learn what&apos;s next.
        p Read anywhere. Cancel anytime
        a.btn.btn-xl(href='#')
          | Try 30 days free 
          i.fas.fa-chevron-right.btn-icon
  
    section.tabs
      .container
        // inclue id for items to handle in JavaScript
        #tab-1.tab-item.tab-border
          i.fas.fa-door-open.fa-3x
          // class hide-sm will hide the item in small screen
          p.hide-sm
            | Cancel anytime
        #tab-2.tab-item
          i.fas.fa-tablet-alt.fa-3x
          // class hide-sm will hide the item in small screen
          p.hide-sm Read anywhere
        #tab-3.tab-item
          i.fas.fa-tags.fa-3x
          // class hide-sm will hide the item in small screen
          p.hide-sm Pick your price

    section.tab-content
      .container
        // Tab content 1
        #tab-1-content.tab-content-item.show
          .tab-1-content-inner
            div
              p.text-lg
                | If you decide Bookflix isn&apos;t for you - no problem. No commitment. Cancel online anytime.
              a.btn.btn-lg(href='#') try 30 days free
            img(src='./uploads/features/tab-content-1.png', alt='content')
        // Tab content 2
        #tab-2-content.tab-content-item
          .tab-2-content-top
            p.text-lg
              | Read books and magazines anytime, anywhere &mdash; personalized for you.
            a.btn.btn-lg(href='#') try 30 days free
          .tab-2-content-bottom
            div
              img(src='./uploads/features/tab-content-2-1.png', alt='1')
              p.text-md Read on your large screen
              p.text-dark Smart TVs, PlayStation, Xbox, Chromecast, Apple TV, Blu-ray players and more.
            div
              img(src='./uploads/features/tab-content-2-2.png', alt='1')
              p.text-md Read instantly or download for later
              p.text-dark Available on phone and tablet, wherever you go.
            div
              img(src='./uploads/features/tab-content-2-3.png', alt='1')
              p.text-md Use any computer
              p.text-dark Watch right on Netflix.com.
